    "Differences in the Θ Richness between patients and healthy networks were also found to be inconsistent across subjects (Fig. 1e; see also Figs.",
    "As a final step, we inspected signals from the same regions belonging to the DMN of both patients and control subjects, again finding no clear traces of tumoral damage in DMN functional signals (Fig. 1f).",
    "In summary, functional signals from tumors and DMNs did not show significant changes in terms of complexity.",
    "However, they displayed alterations both in the power domain and in the distribution of functional connections.",
